msgctxt "talk02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>The thing is...<2.pa>just the other day, one of\n"
"our customers said he saw a <3.se_co>white horse<4.re_co>\n"
"on <5.se_co>Safula Hill <6.re_co>recently...\n"
"<7.so>Could it be a relative of the royal family's\n"
"<8.se_co>white horse <9.re_co>from my grandfather's day?\n"
"\n"
"Well, if you happen to see a <10.se_co>white horse<11.re_co>\n"
"on your travels,<12.pa> do you think you could\n"
"bring it back to me?<13.ch>"
msgstr ""

