msgid ""
"<1.so>Thank you!<2.pa> If you see the <3.se_co>white horse<4.re_co>,\n"
"please <5.se_co>register it <6.re_co>at a stable and bring\n"
"it to me.\n"
"<7.so>The <8.se_co>white horse <9.re_co>on <10.se_co>Safula "
"Hill<11.re_co>\n"
"supposedly has a beautiful, pure-white\n"
"coat without any mottling.\n"
"I hear it's very elusive, though.\n"
"Good luck."
msgstr ""

