msgctxt "talk10"
msgid ""
"<1.so>The <2.se_co>white horse <3.re_co>on <4.se_co>Safula Hill<5.re_co>\n"
"supposedly has a beautiful pure-white\n"
"coat without any mottling...\n"
"They say it roams by itself,<6.pa> apart\n"
"from other groups of horses.\n"
"\n"
"If you end up finding it and <7.se_co>registering it<8.re_co>\n"
"at a stable, I'd really love to see it.\n"
"Thanks."
msgstr ""

