"<6.se_co>Zelda<7.re_co>\n"
"rode. The one my grandfather told me\n"
"about when I was little...\n"
"<8.so>The sight of the princess riding atop the\n"
"<9.se_co>white horse <10.re_co>was supposed to be a beauty\n"
"beyond words...\n"
"<11.so>There's no doubt about it, this <12.se_co>horse<13.re_co> is\n"
"the grandchild of that horse of long ago.<14.pa>\n"
"So beautiful...<15.pa> So pure...<16.pa>"
